Dropbox (store, sync and share files online)

Dropbox is a free service that lets you bring all your photos, docs,
and videos anywhere. This means that any file you save to your
Dropbox folder will be automatically shared with all your computers,
phones and the Dropbox website.

===============
==  WARNING  ==
===============

Version 3.x has started using local QT5 libraries for the UI.
The current version still does not show the tray icons well or at all.
The synchronization engine is not effected by it and even if there is
no tray icon the synchronization works.
